    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few light surface scratches and minor stone chips upon close inspection. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. You can expect a solid, dependable car that looks great and performs well in all standard driving conditions.",
