    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and budget-friendly find! This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion, offering a solid driving experience for anyone looking for great value. While it shows some honest signs of use and age, it remains a sturdy choice for your daily commutes or weekend errands. It's a practical, no-nonsense car that\u2019s ready to get to work for its next owner!",
      "price": 18500.0,
