      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and a lifetime of being strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a meticulously organized binder of every service record since new. This is a rare, collector-grade specimen that has been obsessively maintained for the most discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
